Subject: [PATCH] Exp 2: Opaque factory dock TermSurf AppIcon ladder

Regenerate TermSurf.appiconset and AppIconImage from brand factory dock
master (cyan #1BFEFF on opaque navy #07203A). Corners are solid dock navy
(alpha 255) instead of transparent-edge composites.
